Nestled against the backdrop of the Nevada Mountains and Nevada Mountain Trail, this upgraded 2-story townhouse offers the perfect blend of modern living and natural beauty. Notice the attention to detail and craftsmanship that sets this home apart. The first floor boasts a stunning upgrade with wood tile flooring, providing both durability and a touch of rustic elegance. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting space for entertaining family and friends.The kitchen features luxurious granite countertops that provide ample workspace for your culinary endeavors. Upgraded appliances and stylish cabinetry complete the space, making it a chef's paradise. If you're seeking a serene retreat with modern comforts and breathtaking views, schedule your visit today and experience the magic of this exceptional property.
